09162907/VYNL-Frame-Raw-Toptube-Badge-31-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09162907/VYNL-Frame-Raw-Toptube-Badge-31-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09162907/VYNL-Frame-Raw-Toptube-Badge-31-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09162907/VYNL-Frame-Raw-Toptube-Badge-31-1536x1024.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09162907/VYNL-Frame-Raw-Toptube-Badge-31-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09162907/VYNL-Frame-Raw-Toptube-Badge-31-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09162907/VYNL-Frame-Raw-Toptube-Badge-31-1920x1280.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09162907/VYNL-Frame-Raw-Toptube-Badge-31-630x420.jpg 630w\"></p><h3>Keeping it Local: VYNL Bikes’ New Virtue</h3><p>According to the company’s PR, Clauson and his wife, Sabrina, intend to operate VYNL as an intimate shop in bike-centric Boulder. Though they don’t promise to source every part from inside the city limits, they commit to U.S.-based manufacturing.</p><p>With regional production, the brand seeks to keep development and delivery nimble. It emphasizes its goal of getting handmade frames to market with reasonable turnaround times.</p><p>“In the context of the world’s crazy current events, U.S. production also allows us to have bikes, in stock, <em>[sic] </em>and ready to ship without the restraints of the global supply chain,” Max said.</p><p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09163340/VYNL-Frame-Pink-Seattube-Badge-3.jpg