kes-Road-White-Front-Angle1.jpg 1999w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09163236/VYNLBikes-Road-White-Front-Angle1-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09163236/VYNLBikes-Road-White-Front-Angle1-800x534.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09163236/VYNLBikes-Road-White-Front-Angle1-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09163236/VYNLBikes-Road-White-Front-Angle1-768x513.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09163236/VYNLBikes-Road-White-Front-Angle1-1536x1025.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09163236/VYNLBikes-Road-White-Front-Angle1-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09163236/VYNLBikes-Road-White-Front-Angle1-1068x713.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09163236/VYNLBikes-Road-White-Front-Angle1-1920x1281.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09163236/VYNLBikes-Road-White-Front-Angle1-629x420.jpg 629w\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-264786\">VYNL Road Disc</figcaption></figure><p>If the brand’s immediate expansion on relaunch is any indication, prototypes could fly relatively hard and fast <span>— </span>if VYNL regains its stability. Taking a year off is a challenge for any manufacturer, and the Clausons put their noses firmly to the grindstone by keeping it local. But they see their situation as an advantage.</p><blockquote><p>“Boulder also has a great ecosystem of partners for us to leverage as we grow this business,” Max said. “We feel very lucky to be based here and are excited for VYNL to put down deep roots into the community.”</p></blockquote><figure id=\"attachment_264790\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-264790\"><img loading=\"eager\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09164230/blog_max_sabrina.png?ezimgfmt=rs%3Adevice%2Frscb25-1\" alt=\"max and sabrina clauson vynl bike owners\" width=\"1000\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb25 src ng ngcb25 srcset\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-264790\">new VYNL owners Sabrina and Max Clausen</figcaption></figure><h3>VYNL Availability and Options</h3><p>The new VYNL Bikes <a href=\"https://www.vynlbikes.com/\">website</a> and ordering process is now live. Customers can choose from 21 paint choices and two decal options for each of the 3 frames.</p><figure id=\"attachment_264788\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-264788\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09163518/VYNLBikes-Road-Blue-Side-Profile.jpg\" alt=\"vynl bikes road rim frame blue\" width=\"1999\" height=\"1333\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09163518/VYNLBikes-Road-Blue-Side-Profile.jpg 1999w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09163518/VYNLBikes-Road-Blue-Side-Profile-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09163518/VYNLBikes-Road-Blue-Side-Profile-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09163518/VYNLBikes-Road-Blue-Side-Profile-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/09163518/VYNLBikes-Road-Blue-Side-Profile-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/w